## Writing Guidelines

### Be Concise

```
✅ "Add to reading list"
❌ "Click here to add this book to your personal reading list"
```

### Be Clear

```
✅ "Your password must be at least 8 characters"
❌ "Password validation failed: minimum length requirement not met"
```

### Be Helpful

```
✅ "No books found. Try searching for a different title."
❌ "No results."
```

## UI Text Patterns

### Buttons

| Action Type | Pattern | Example |
|-------------|---------|---------|
| Primary action | Verb | "Save", "Create", "Submit" |
| Navigation | Destination | "Go to Dashboard" |
| Destructive | Confirm action | "Delete Book" |

### Error Messages

Structure: What happened + What to do

```
✅ "We couldn't save your changes. Please try again."
❌ "Error 500: Internal Server Error"
```

### Empty States

Structure: What's missing + How to fix

```
✅ "No books in your library yet. Add your first book to get started."
❌ "No data available"
```

### Success Messages

Structure: What happened + What's next (optional)

```
✅ "Book added to your reading list!"
✅ "Settings saved. Changes will take effect immediately."
```

